Summary: Scalable, high-performance, open source NoSQL database
Name: mongodb
Version: @@VERSION@@
Source0: @@UPSTREAM@@
Release: 1
BuildRequires: scons,openssl-devel,glibc-devel
License: AGPL 3.0
Group: Applications/Databases

%description 
MongoDB (from "humongous") is a scalable, high-performance, open
source NoSQL database. Written in C++, MongoDB features:
. 
 Document-Oriented Storage
 Full Index Support
 Replication & High Availability
 Auto-Sharding
 Querying
 Fast In-Place Updates
 Map/Reduce
 GridFS

%prep
# %setup -q -n mongodb-src-r%{version}
%setup -D -q -n mongodb-src-r%{version}
%patch -P 001 -p2
%patch -P 002 -p2

%build
/usr/bin/scons --ssl --prefix=%{buildroot}/usr

%install
/usr/bin/scons --ssl --prefix=%{buildroot}/usr install

%clean
rm -rf %{buildroot}

%files
%defattr(-,root,root,-)
%doc README APACHE-2.0.txt GNU-AGPL-3.0.txt
%{_bindir}/*
/usr/include/mongo/*
/usr/lib/libmongoclient.a

%changelog
